## Data Attribution

Earthquake data displayed in this visualization may come from various sources:
- Myanmar Department of Meteorology and Hydrology
- USGS Earthquake Hazards Program
- Regional seismological networks

Please cite the appropriate data sources when using this visualization for 
research or publication purposes.

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and informational purposes only. 
The earthquake data and visualizations should not be used as the sole basis 
for emergency response or critical decision-making. Always consult official 
sources and local authorities for accurate and timely earthquake information.
